<h1>Voice API</h1>
<p>The Voice API provides Text-to-Speech (TTS), Speech-to-Text (STT), and Voice Agent capabilities. WebSocket endpoints are not proxied through progrok — use ephemeral tokens for direct client connections instead.</p>
